Package: libdtkmultimedia
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Development Tool Kit multimedia library
 libdtkmultimedia is base library of Deepin Qt/C++ applications.
 .
 This package contains the shared libraries.

Package: libdtkmultimedia-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libdtkmultimedia( =${binary:Version})
Description: Development Tool Kit multimedia devel library
 libdtkmultimedia-dev is base devel library of Deepin Qt/C++ applications.
 .
 This package contains the header files and static libraries.

